# Inventory Rules

- Never allow stock to go negative unless product policy explicitly permits backorders.
- Use reservation-first flow for checkout; commit deduction only on final confirmation.
- Treat inventory updates as concurrency-sensitive (locking/atomic updates/version checks).
- Keep warehouse/location-aware inventory logic explicit.
- Inventory adjustments must include reason codes and actor metadata.
